* Balance of Payments :econ:
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       f00af8a3-14a3-4aa3-aa48-6d7fe943017b
:END:

Summarises the economic transactions of an [[id:908979e3-4240-4b4d-ad02-62e08dcc0795][Economy]] with the outside world.
There are 3 parts to balance of payments:
+ [[id:a200bf07-fbdd-4a84-8e5a-e416acefd153][Current Account]]
+ [[id:6962990a-d57f-4167-94e0-a4bc15e686c9][Capital Account]]
+ [[id:bce8032f-89e7-4d46-8d91-50123785d361][Financial Account]]
